CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1780653972
OL,3,CStarmer accuses Musk of 'trying to
OL,4,Cwhip up division' over Henry Nowak's
OL,5,Cmurder
OL,7,FMr Nowak's killer Vickrum Digwa
OL,8,Fclaimed he had been the victim of a
OL,9,Fracial attack. While Mr Nowak was
OL,10,Fhandcuffed by police who ignored his
OL,11,Fpleas that he could not breathe as he
OL,12,Flay dying.
OL,14,FThe prime minister has urged
OL,15,Fpoliticians to heed Mr Nowak's
OL,16,Frelatives' calls not to use the case
OL,17,F"to cause disturbances", as he
OL,18,Fcriticised Musk, who has offered to
OL,19,Ffund a private prosecution of
OL,20,FHampshire Constabulary, and branded
OL,21,FNigel Farage's response "unforgivable".
OL,26,@yD@AOUyD@WO]}D@YOU}D@fO]
