PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1780653972
OL,3,CStarmer accuses Musk of 'trying to
OL,4,Cwhip up division' over Henry Nowak's
OL,5,Cmurder
OL,7,FStarmer, who will meet Mr Nowak's
OL,8,Ffamily on Thursday, said: "We need to
OL,9,Falso assert who we are as a country,
OL,10,Fbecause Musk, again, has been
OL,11,Finterfering in our politics in the
OL,12,Flast few days, trying to whip up
OL,13,Fdivision ` that is not who we are in
OL,14,FBritain."
OL,16,FStarmer continued: "In Britain, we are
OL,17,Freasonable, tolerant people.
OL,19,F"When we have a terrible case like
OL,20,FHenry's case, Henry Nowak, we react
OL,21,Fcalmly, as his family have done."
OL,26,@pD@[OUxD@TOU{D@AOU}D@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/19
