OL,3,CStarmer accuses Musk of 'trying to
OL,4,Cwhip up division' over Henry Nowak's
OL,5,Cmurder
OL,7,FThe Conservatives have called for the
OL,8,Fofficers who arrested Mr Nowak on
OL,9,Ffalse racism claims to face a full
OL,10,Fmisconduct investigation.
OL,12,FAsked about the Tories' demand,
OL,13,FStarmer said "there are questions that
OL,14,Fneed to be answered" over the police
OL,15,Fresponse, and added that the
OL,16,FIndependent Office for Police Conduct
OL,17,Fshould be given space to "get on with
OL,18,Ftheir job" in investigating the case.
OL,26,@uD@NOUvD@TO]yD@ZOUzD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/19
