OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1780653972
OL,3,CStarmer accuses Musk of 'trying to
OL,4,Cwhip up division' over Henry Nowak's
OL,5,Cmurder
OL,7,FShe wrote on X: "They have asked that
OL,8,Fwe work across political parties and
OL,9,Freligions to rebuild trust in the
OL,10,Fpolice. That trust has been broken
OL,11,Fbecause of what happened, and I agree
OL,12,Fwith them on that.
OL,14,F"We must also be prepared to examine,
OL,15,Fcarefully and seriously, religious
OL,16,Fpractices or exemptions that permit
OL,17,Fthe carrying of dangerous weapons in
OL,18,Fpublic, and other activities that are
OL,19,Fnot conducive to the public good. We
OL,20,Falso need to examine where the law
OL,21,Fneeds to change."
OL,26,@oD@QOUvD@AOU}D@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/19
