OL,3,CStarmer accuses Musk of 'trying to
OL,4,Cwhip up division' over Henry Nowak's
OL,5,Cmurder
OL,7,FMrs Badenoch added that the family
OL,8,Fagreed with her that "we need to bring
OL,9,Fcommon sense back" to how equality is
OL,10,Ftreated under the law.
OL,12,FShe has previously called for an end
OL,13,Fto "two-tier policing" and to
OL,14,F"terrible anti-racism training" for
OL,15,Fpolice, "which is just reverse racism".
OL,17,FMeanwhile, Reform MP Robert Jenrick
OL,18,Fsaid it was "ludicrous" to suggest
OL,19,Fthat Mr Farage's response to the
OL,20,Fmurder was stoking division.
