OL,3,CStarmer accuses Musk of 'trying to
OL,4,Cwhip up division' over Henry Nowak's
OL,5,Cmurder
OL,7,FA spokesperson from the party has
OL,8,Fconfirmed that Reform UK have been in
OL,9,Fcontact with Henry Nowak's family to
OL,10,F"express our condolences and hope to
OL,11,Fmeet them soon".
OL,13,FThe leader of the police watchdog has
OL,14,Furged people to stop speculating about
OL,15,Fthe murder of teenager Henry Nowak.
OL,17,FIndependent Officer for Police Conduct
OL,18,F(IOPC) Derrick Campbell said late on
OL,19,FWednesday: "We are acutely aware of
OL,20,Fthe public interest in this case.
OL,26,@{D@LOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/19
