OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1780653972
OL,3,CStarmer accuses Musk of 'trying to
OL,4,Cwhip up division' over Henry Nowak's
OL,5,Cmurder
OL,7,F"We would respectfully ask people to
OL,8,Fstop speculating on an ongoing live
OL,9,Finvestigation.
OL,11,F"This investigation is going to fully
OL,12,Festablish the circumstances of the
OL,13,Fcase including whether there may be
OL,14,Fmisconduct on the part of any of the
OL,15,Fofficers involved.
OL,17,F"The ongoing commentary about the
OL,18,Fevidence and speculation risks
OL,19,Fprejudicing any potential processes
OL,20,Fand preventing Henry Nowak's family
OL,21,Fgetting the answers they deserve."
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUyD@AOU}D@bO]
