CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1780653972
OL,3,CStarmer accuses Musk of 'trying to
OL,4,Cwhip up division' over Henry Nowak's
OL,5,Cmurder
OL,7,FSpeaking outside court after the
OL,8,Fverdict on Monday, Mr Nowak's father,
OL,9,FMark, had said that his family wanted
OL,10,Fto use Henry's story "to make change
OL,11,Ffor the better" rather than as fuel
OL,12,Ffor conflict.
OL,14,F"We do not want his death to be used
OL,15,Fto create further division, hatred or
OL,16,Ftension. We want his story to help
OL,17,Fmake our streets safer for everyone,"
OL,18,Fhe said.
OL,26,@vD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/19
