OL,3,CStarmer accuses Musk of 'trying to
OL,4,Cwhip up division' over Henry Nowak's
OL,5,Cmurder
OL,7,FDespite pleas for calm, hundreds
OL,8,Fgathered outside Southampton Central
OL,9,FPolice Station shortly before 6pm on
OL,10,FTuesday, where Tommy Robinson and
OL,11,FLaurence Fox were among those who
OL,12,Fspoke to the crowd.
OL,14,FITV News Correspondent Neil Connery
OL,15,Freported live at the scene
OL,17,FViolent scenes broke out after a large
OL,18,Fgroup walked across town to the
OL,19,FPortswood area.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
