OL,3,CStarmer accuses Musk of 'trying to
OL,4,Cwhip up division' over Henry Nowak's
OL,5,Cmurder
OL,7,FChairs, cans and flares were thrown at
OL,8,Fpolice in riot gear, eventually
OL,9,Fforcing officers and three police vans
OL,10,Fback from the line they had been
OL,11,Fholding.
OL,13,FThe National Police Chiefs' Council
OL,14,F(NPCC) said it would review anti-
OL,15,Fracism guidance ` which advises police
OL,16,Fto treat ethnic minorities differently
OL,17,Fto get them better outcomes ` that
OL,18,Fsome have blamed for the actions of
OL,19,Fthe officers who arrested Mr Nowak.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
