OL,5,Cmurder
OL,7,FThe policing minister called the
OL,8,Flanguage in the document "clumsy" and
OL,9,Fadded, "it gives the wrong impression
OL,10,Fand needs to be changed".
OL,12,FThe Conservatives said "the race
OL,13,Faction plan needs to go" despite it
OL,14,Fbeing introduced while they were in
OL,15,Fgovernment.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/19
